title: Phlogistonic Regulator
type: text/vnd.tiddlywiki

A layer of insulation within your armor protects you from rapid temperature fluctuations. 

You gain resistance equal to half your level to <<tag Cold>> and <<tag Fire>> damage. When under the effects of [[Overdrive]], the resistance increases by 2.